@startuml
title Sơ đồ tuần tự - Chức năng đổi mật khẩu

actor "Người dùng" as User
boundary "_ChangePasswordScreenState" as ChangePasswordScreenState
control "TokenStorageService" as TokenStorageService
control "AuthApiService" as AuthApiService
control "AuthController" as AuthController
control "AuthServiceImpl" as AuthServiceImpl
control "SecurityContextHolder" as SecurityContextHolder
database "UserRepository" as UserRepository
control "PasswordEncoder" as PasswordEncoder
control "Navigator" as Navigator

User -> ChangePasswordScreenState: 1: nhập mật khẩu hiện tại, mật khẩu mới và bấm Cập nhật mật khẩu
activate ChangePasswordScreenState

ChangePasswordScreenState -> ChangePasswordScreenState: 2: _submit()
activate ChangePasswordScreenState

ChangePasswordScreenState -> ChangePasswordScreenState: 3: _validateFields()
activate ChangePasswordScreenState
deactivate ChangePasswordScreenState

ChangePasswordScreenState -> TokenStorageService: 4: gọi
activate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService -> TokenStorageService: 5: getToken()
activate TokenStorageService
deactivate TokenStorageService
TokenStorageService --> ChangePasswordScreenState: 6: trả về kết quả
deactivate TokenStorageService

ChangePasswordScreenState -> AuthApiService: 7: gọi
activate AuthApiService
AuthApiService -> AuthApiService: 8: changePassword(token, ChangePasswordRequest)
activate AuthApiService

AuthApiService -> AuthController: 9: gọi API POST /auth/change-password
activate AuthController
AuthController -> AuthController: 10: changePassword(ChangePasswordRequest)
activate AuthController

AuthController -> AuthServiceImpl: 11: gọi
activate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl -> AuthServiceImpl: 12: changePassword(ChangePasswordRequest)
activate AuthServiceImpl

AuthServiceImpl -> SecurityContextHolder: 13: gọi
activate SecurityContextHolder
SecurityContextHolder -> SecurityContextHolder: 14: getContext().getAuthentication().getName()
activate SecurityContextHolder
deactivate SecurityContextHolder
SecurityContextHolder --> AuthServiceImpl: 15: trả về kết quả
deactivate SecurityContextHolder

AuthServiceImpl -> UserRepository: 16: gọi
activate UserRepository
UserRepository -> UserRepository: 17: findByEmailAndActive(email, true)
activate UserRepository
deactivate UserRepository
UserRepository --> AuthServiceImpl: 18: trả về kết quả
deactivate UserRepository

AuthServiceImpl -> PasswordEncoder: 19: gọi
activate PasswordEncoder
PasswordEncoder -> PasswordEncoder: 20: matches(oldPassword, userPassword)
activate PasswordEncoder
deactivate PasswordEncoder
PasswordEncoder --> AuthServiceImpl: 21: trả về kết quả
deactivate PasswordEncoder

AuthServiceImpl -> PasswordEncoder: 22: gọi
activate PasswordEncoder
PasswordEncoder -> PasswordEncoder: 23: encode(newPassword)
activate PasswordEncoder
deactivate PasswordEncoder
PasswordEncoder --> AuthServiceImpl: 24: trả về kết quả
deactivate PasswordEncoder

deactivate AuthServiceImpl
AuthServiceImpl --> AuthController: 25: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthServiceImpl

deactivate AuthController
AuthController --> AuthApiService: 26: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthController

deactivate AuthApiService
AuthApiService --> ChangePasswordScreenState: 27: trả về kết quả
deactivate AuthApiService

ChangePasswordScreenState -> Navigator: 28: gọi
activate Navigator
Navigator -> Navigator: 29: pop(context)
activate Navigator
deactivate Navigator
Navigator --> ChangePasswordScreenState: 30: trả về kết quả
deactivate Navigator

deactivate ChangePasswordScreenState

ChangePasswordScreenState --> User: 31: điều hướng về màn hình trước
deactivate ChangePasswordScreenState

@enduml
